column2: PORC_ADM4 <- ggplot(SANTIAGO,aes(x = cluster4,y = PORC_ADM)) + geom_boxplot() + labs(title = "Porcentaje adultos mayores por zona"                , x = "Cluster", y = "Porcentaje") + geom_hline(aes(yintercept = mean(PORC_ADM)),linetype="dotted",size=1.5,color="deeppink1")
